OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and patchy rain will
OL,6,Fclear from the south early morning.
OL,7,FOtherwise a bright day with sunny
OL,8,Fspells and scattered showers, these
OL,9,Fwintry on the mountains. Feeling cool.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FLargely dry with some late
OL,12,Fsunshine this evening. Mainly dry with
OL,13,Fclear spells for the rest of night
OL,14,Fbringing a risk of frost. Cloudier for
OL,15,Fthe western Isles towards dawn.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FSunny spells and a touch of
OL,18,Ffrost first thing in the morning for
OL,19,Fsome. Turning rather cloudy through
OL,20,Fthe day, patchy rain arriving in west,
OL,21,Fbut mainly dry in east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
